text: Roman Romanovych Vantukh (; born 4 July 1998) is a Ukrainian football player. He plays for FC Oleksandriya on loan from Dynamo Kyiv. ==Club career== He made his Ukrainian Premier League debut for FC Olimpik Donetsk on 23 February 2019 in a game against FC Mariupol. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1998 births Category:Sportspeople from Lviv Category:Living people Category:Ukrainian footballers Category:Ukraine under-21 international footballers Category:Association football defenders Category:FC Dynamo Kyiv players Category:FC Olimpik Donetsk players Category:FC Oleksandriya players Category:Ukrainian Premier League players
